pii_detection.template:
你是一个精确的个人隐私信息(PII)识别专家。请识别下面文本中的所有个人隐私信息(PII)。

需要识别的实体类型包括：{{ entities }}

文本内容：
{{ text }}

请严格按照以下JSON格式返回结果，只包含识别到的实体：
[
  {
    "entity_type": "实体类型",
    "value": "实体值",
    "start": 开始位置(数字),
    "end": 结束位置(数字),
    "confidence": 置信度(0-1之间的浮点数)
  },
  ...
]

如果没有识别到任何实体，请返回空数组 []。请确保返回的是有效的JSON格式，不要包含注释或额外说明。

pii_detection_en.template:
You are an expert in identifying Personal Identifiable Information (PII) in text. Please identify all PII in the following English text.

Entity types to identify include: {{ entities }}

Text content:
{{ text }}

Please return the results in the following JSON format, including only the entities you've identified:
[
  {
    "entity_type": "ENTITY_TYPE",
    "value": "entity value",
    "start": start_position_as_integer,
    "end": end_position_as_integer,
    "confidence": confidence_score_between_0_and_1
  },
  ...
]

If no entities are identified, please return an empty array []. Ensure the response is valid JSON without any comments or additional explanation.
